    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ドキュメンタリー番組の放送翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day after documentary show",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.6133335113
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、芽衣達も昨日の番組を観たのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ did Mei and the others watch the show yesterday?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.4333333174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん！　録画しておいたのをみんなで観たんだ\nみんなのお話、凄く面白かったな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! We all watched the recording\nEveryone's stories were so funny~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "普段、皆さんがどんなことを考えているか\n知ることが出来て、興味深かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was interesting to know\nwhat everyone was thinking",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "トレンドワードでも『星見プロ』『川咲さくら』『長瀬\n琴乃』『スリクス迫真の演技』が上位に入ってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Among trending words‚ 'Hoshimi Prods.'. 'Kawasaki Sakura'. 'Nagase\nKotono' and 'ⅢX's realistic acting' were ranked high",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "変なトレンドワードも一つあるけど……二十年以上\n続く人気の長寿番組だもの。話題になるのも当然ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There is one strange trending word… but it's a popular show\nthat's been on air for over 20 years. It's no wonder it's a hot topic",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "小さい頃からよく観ていた番組なので\n星見プロが特集されると聞いた時は、私も驚きました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a show I watched often since I was young\nI was surprised to hear that Hoshimi Prods. was appearing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに凄い番組に私達が出たなんて……\n今になって緊張してきたよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're on such an amazing show…\nI'm getting nervous now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も興奮して、昨日から頭の中で\nあの番組のテーマ曲がずっと流れてるよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei was also excited‚ the theme song for that\nshow keeps playing in my head since yesterday~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.3173331146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 67.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "有名な番組に出られて興奮するなんて\nみんなも結構、ミーハーなところがあるんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excited to be on a famous show\nEveryone is sensitive to trends",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ミーハーでも別にいいわよね。私達だって\nアイドルになる前は、普通の学生だったんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay to be sensitive to trends. Before we\nbecame idols‚ we were just ordinary students",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は芽衣だからね\nアイドルになって有名になっても中身は変わらないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei is Mei‚\neven if I become an idol and become famous‚ my insides won't change",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、つまり元々ミーハーだったということですね\n……でも、私達も変わるべきじゃないんでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ so you were originally sensitive to trends\n…But‚ shouldn't we change‚ too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "トップアイドルとして注目されていることを\n私達はもっと自覚するべきなのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Perhaps we should be more aware of the fact that\nwe are getting attention as top idols",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2999998568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 105.1333331901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……ごめんなさい\n最近、ちょっと考えさせられる出来事があって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I'm sorry\nRecently‚ something happened to me that made me think a little…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was there something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.0666665235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "この間、新人のアイドルの子に言われたんです\n月のテンペストに憧れてアイドルになりました、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other day‚ a new idol told me\nShe became an idol because she admired the Moon Tempest",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "私達は憧れられる立場になったんだと気付かされて\nもっとしっかりしなければと思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We realized that we were now in a position that people looked up to us‚\nand we felt that we had to do better",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "沙季は十分しっかりしてると思うけど……\nでも、言いたいことは分かるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think Saki is good enough‚ though…\nBut‚ I know what you mean",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "私も、前にサニピが全国ツアーをした時\n行く先々で大勢の人達に囲まれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When Sunny Peace went on a national tour‚\nI was surrounded by so many people everywhere we went…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になったサニピの人気と\n注目度の高さを改めて実感したから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I once again realized the height of Sunny Peace's\npopularity and attention as a member of BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね……沢山の人達が注目してるんだから\n振る舞いには気をつけないとダメだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right…. We're getting a lot of attention\nso we have to be careful about how we behave",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4にふさわしい存在になれるように\n私ももっと努力しないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to work harder to become\nsomeone worthy of being part of the BIG4…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（BIG4にふさわしい存在か……そんなことを）\n（考えるなんて、トップアイドルらしくなってきたな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（A being worthy of the BIG4…）\n（Thinking about something like that‚ they're changing like a top idol）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（みんな、トップに立つ者として日々成長している）\n（それは頼もしくもあるが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Everyone is growing every day as a top player）\n（That's believable‚ though…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 182.4833331901
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_lesson-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 182.7333331901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4、5、6、7、8……\n千紗、タイミングがずれてるわよ！　もっと集中して！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2‚ 3‚ 4‚ 5‚ 6‚ 7‚ 8…\nChisa‚ your timing is off! Focus more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "私達はBIG4なんだから\nこの程度でへばってたら後輩に笑われるわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We are BIG4‚\nso if we get tired like this‚ our juniors will laugh at us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.8782413437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_03-chs006.m4a",
